query:
SELECT c.id, c.name, c.relationship, c.flags,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contactPhones WHERE contactId = c.id) as phone_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contactEmails WHERE contactId = c.id) as email_count
FROM contacts c
WHERE c.propertyId = 750033;
